{"tid":1789712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"\"頭條\" 唔講HSBC, 换上\"英資\" 去形容。。。","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:27:11.000Z","uid":197197,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97f3814a1db2981c61aeeec8ffa7a3775d510fba","tid":1789712,"uid":197197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1664307/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1664307%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=7c7d187d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1664307%2F&h=4d416650\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1664307/</a><br />\n<br />\n我知道大家會問，點解我要放&quot;頭條&quot; 出黎？ 但首先唔好理佢係咩野先<br />\n<br />\n重點係大家講緊HSBC, 點解佢咁得意有HSBC唔講，要用&quot;英資&quot; 去做形容詞？？？答案好明顯<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以冷靜，點都好，小弟真係唔支持裝修HSBC, 佢依個報導好明顯想有話題比人講，就係示威者依家已經根本唔會理親中或唔親中，總知就只會破壞等等。。。<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望大家冷靜，另一方面，岩岩星火都出左聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2634390273514755&amp;id=1965117443775378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2634390273514755%26id%3D1965117443775378&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=705bac0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2634390273514755&amp;id=1965117443775378</a><br />\n<br />\n所以大家要冷靜，唔好衝動，一方面不要中計。另一方面比時間星火去處理，我地依家可以做，就係不要同星火割蓆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8728c7dd63e32fb100a63c5d1ecef5cfff9289ec","tid":1789712,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到